55.7	Clash_of_Civilizations	The Clash of Civilizations	The Clash of Civilizations is a theory, proposed by political scientist Samuel P. Huntington, that people's cultural and religious identities will be the primary source of conflict in the post-Cold War world.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b9/Clash_civilizations.jpg/200px-Clash_civilizations.jpg
